  "title": "HR Intern/ Contract HR Assistant (3-6months)",
  "description": "<p><strong>About the Role:</strong><br />We are looking for an HR Intern/Contract HR Assistant to support our Human Resources team. You will gain hands-on experience in HR operations and learn about various HR functions in a small team environment.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Assist with recruitment: post job openings, coordinate interviews, and communicate with candidates</li><li>Prepare standard HR letters such as confirmation letters and certification of employment</li><li>File and maintain non-sensitive employee records, including personal details, training certificates, leave, and attendance records</li><li>Support onboarding and HR projects</li><li>Provide ad-hoc HR support as assigned by the HR Director</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Currently studying in HR, Business, or related field</li><li>Good communication and organizational skills</li><li>Proficient in Microsoft Office</li></ul>",
